The nanohydrophobicity was then quantified using the colored vGNP. The nanohydrophobicity of a vGNP can be calculated as:1logG/R=log∑Ihydrophobicity∑Ihydrophilicity\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
